author: The Critical Drinker
description:
Got a question? Then ask the Drinker, because we're getting festive with this one. I'll be hanging out for a couple of hours, drinking shots and putting the world to rights. 

Wanna go to the premiere of MauLer's short film? Then click the link to reserve your ticket: https://www.eventbrite.co.uk/e/all-in-good-time-an-evening-with-the-drinker-tickets-1978885560983?aff=oddtdtcreator
title: Ask The Drinker - Christmas Special!
